      <title>罗德岛社会服务门户网站遭网络犯罪分子入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/rhode-island-social-services-portal-breached-by-cybercriminals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗德岛州用于管理公共福利的计算机系统遭到黑客攻击，黑客威胁称，如果不支付费用，他们就会公布个人数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/rhode-island-social-services-portal-breached-by-cybercriminals</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 23:37:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 鹰派被任命，特朗普立场模糊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/helberg-and-rubio-backed-tiktok-ban-get-trump-nod-for-top-state-department-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些在美国对 TikTok 批评最激烈的人将在下一届特朗普政府中担任高级职位，以平衡这位新任总统在这款受欢迎的中国应用程序面临美国禁令之际对其采取的开放态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/helberg-and-rubio-backed-tiktok-ban-get-trump-nod-for-top-state-department-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 16:58:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将于周五在海湖庄园与苹果公司总裁蒂姆·库克共进晚餐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/trump-to-dine-with-apple-s-tim-cook-at-mar-a-lago-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普将于周五会见苹果公司首席执行官蒂姆·库克，这是候任总统与科技公司高管之间一系列会谈中的最新一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/trump-to-dine-with-apple-s-tim-cook-at-mar-a-lago-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 01:43:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Iconiq Growth 在 ServiceTitan 首次公开募股中筹资逾 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/iconiq-growth-gains-more-than-1-billion-in-servicetitan-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，科技初创公司 ServiceTitan Inc. 本周在公开市场首次亮相，为早期投资者带来了巨额收益 - Iconiq Growth 获得了超过 10 亿美元的回报，Bessemer Venture Partners 获得了超过 8 亿美元的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/iconiq-growth-gains-more-than-1-billion-in-servicetitan-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 01:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
